            <h2>First Class For Frontier</h2>

            <p>As of now, <b>First Class</b> tickets are not available for Frontier Airlines as they are scheduled to be added only in the latter part of the present year, 2025. The airlines intends to provide the most luxurious experience to travellers who will be opting for this class of service when it is available.</p>

            <p>Travellers can hope to enjoy adequate leg space and more comfortable seats that can be adjusted with the advent of this option. These seats will be available in the first two rows of the flight which shall be provided with new fittings.</p>

            <h2>The Alternative to First Class</h2>

            <p>Since Frontier Airlines does not offer either First or <b>Business class</b> of service, the most comfortable alternative to these options are the premium Stretch seats that are available in the exit row or near the bulkheads of the flight. These seats possess an adjustable recline, extra legroom and extra seating space providing travellers with all possible comfort.</p>

            <p>Travellers will also find that the middle seats of the airlines are more comfortable than aisle or window seats allowing travellers to enjoy their journey without feeling cramped. All seats of the airlines are laid in a three-by-three format in the economy class of service with blocking of the middle seats for the benefit of premium flyers opting for UpFront Plus. Travellers can enjoy special privileges such as more leg space and the option to choose their seats as well as many other amenities with additional payments.</p>

            <h3>Three Ticketing Options Frontier Airlines First Class</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Basic Fare</li>
                <li>The WORKS</li>
                <li>The PERKS</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These are the three booking options available with the Frontier Airlines Flights First class for the travelers and with these options you can understand frontier does not define any particular fare class such as economy and first class like other airlines. It is a low-cost airline and that’s why only seating can upgrade but fare class is the same thing. Basic fare is the cheapest fare class for Frontier Airlines.</p>

